OL,3,CAntisocial behaviour victims can
OL,4,Cdemand policing review in 'UK first'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FVictims of anti-social behaviour will
OL,8,Fbe able to demand an independent
OL,9,Freview if they are not satisfied with
OL,10,Fhow officers have responded under a
OL,11,Fnew scheme.
OL,13,FPeople living within the area covered
OL,14,Fby Durham Police will be able to
OL,15,Frequest a review if they have reported
OL,16,Fthree or more instances of anti-social
OL,17,Fbehaviour but the offences continue.
OL,19,FIt is considered the first scheme of
OL,20,Fits kind in the country.
