OL,7,FJohn McGee knows more than most about
OL,8,Fthe issue, having said it made him
OL,9,Ffeel nervous to be in his own home.
OL,11,F"There were pitch battles out on the
OL,12,Fstreet," he told ITV News.
OL,14,F"24 hours, seven days a week. Young
OL,15,Fkids coming in and out, up and down
OL,16,Fthe path, smashing doors.
OL,18,F"Rubbish getting thrown out, round the
OL,19,Fback of the house attracting rats. It
OL,20,Fwas just total mayhem.
