OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,F"You started to feel like nobody was
OL,8,Fpaying any attention to you."
OL,10,FIt is stories like Mr McGee's that
OL,11,Fhave inspired Durham Police to act,
OL,12,Fwith Police and Crime Commissioner Joy
OL,13,FAllen launching the scheme on Tuesday.
OL,15,F"Antisocial behaviour can be
OL,16,Frelentless," she said. "Unusually, we
OL,17,Fnow have the right of appeal so we can
OL,18,Fhave a case review and understand what
OL,19,Fwent wrong, why people are still
OL,20,Fstruggling and why it has not been
OL,21,Fnipped in the bud.
