OL,7,F"I think that gives the victim that
OL,8,Freal power to say their voices are
OL,9,Fgoing to be heard."
OL,11,FA more proactive approach has already
OL,12,Fbeen seen in Durham city centre after
OL,13,Fanti-social behaviour plagued the
OL,14,Fmarket hall last September.
OL,16,F"It is nowhere near what it used to
OL,17,Fbe," said Susan Platten, from Brew and
OL,18,FBean.
