OL,7,F"The police are doing I really good
OL,8,Fjob I think - if we do have a problem,
OL,9,Fwe give them a ring and honestly they
OL,10,Fare straight in."
OL,12,FDurham Police has stressed that the
OL,13,Fscheme is designed to help assess
OL,14,Findividual needs rather than push anti-
OL,15,Fsocial behaviour into other areas.
