OL,7,FMr McGee believes it will help tackle
OL,8,Fthe issue, adding: "People were
OL,9,Fstarting to say we are going to move
OL,10,Fout, but I said if you move out you
OL,11,Fare going to find somewhere where you
OL,12,Fhave the same happening again.
OL,14,F"I do think people will start taking
OL,15,Fthings seriously now."
